helptext.en:
Publication Type - When you pick the Publication Type “Volume / Publication Number”, you can enter the volume number in the “Title of the Work”

Other Journal or Publication Name – if the name of the publication does not exist in Journal or Publication Name list, enter the full name here.

Publication Identifier – once you have selected a Journal of Publication Name, enter the Report Number (e.g., enter the Bulletin number if it is a GSC Bulletin), or enter the URL, or enter a DOI with character string divided into a prefix and a suffix separated by a slash (e.g., 10.000/123).
